Topic: {{ topic }}

Return 5-8 Instagram usernames (handles only, no @, no URLs, no numbering) for public creator-led accounts educators or audiences follow for this topic. Mix educators, entertainers, practitioners, and commentators when possible.

Output one comma-separated line of usernames only.

Topic: {{ topic }}

Identify 6-10 real, active subreddits where people passionate about or affected by this topic hang out.

Return ONLY a comma-separated list of subreddit names with no r/ prefix, no explanations, no numbering.

