data.task_description_template:
Topic: {{ topic }}

Research brief:
{{ upstream['merge_signals']['text'] }}

Return strict JSON with one key: trend_opportunities. It must be an array of 3-5 objects matching this shape: title, why_now, audience, evidence, confidence, risk, recommended_platforms.
Each evidence item must include: source, title, url, metric, quote_or_summary, relevance. Use null for missing url or metric. confidence is a number from 0 to 1.

Topic: {{ topic }}

Creator and profile inputs:
{{ upstream['merge_signals']['text'] }}

